<problem>
				  <para>Calculate the electronegativity difference between: <chem_compound>Be</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>C</chem_compound>, <chem_compound>H</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>C</chem_compound>, <chem_compound>Li</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>F</chem_compound>, <chem_compound>Al</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>Na</chem_compound>, <chem_compound>C</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>O</chem_compound>.</para>
			</problem>
