			  <para><chem_compound>Be</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>C</chem_compound>: <latex><number>2.5</number> - <number>1.5</number> = <number>1.0</number>.</latex></para>
			  <para><chem_compound>H</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>C</chem_compound>: <latex><number>2.5</number> - <number>2.1</number> = <number>0.4</number>.</latex></para>
			  <para><chem_compound>Li</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>F</chem_compound>: <latex><number>4.0</number> - <number>1.0</number> = <number>3.0</number>.</latex></para>
			  <para><chem_compound>Al</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>Na</chem_compound>: <latex><number>1.5</number> - <number>0.9</number> = <number>0.6</number>.</latex></para>
			  <para><chem_compound>C</chem_compound> and <chem_compound>O</chem_compound>: <latex><number>3.5</number> - <number>2.5</number> = <number>1.0</number>.</latex></para>
			</solution>
			<correct> <para><number>1.0</number>, <number>0.4</number>, <number>3.0</number>, <number>0.6</number> and <number>1.0</number></para></correct>
