            <section type="subsection">
              <title>Electronegativity and bonding</title>
              <shortcode>ESBMF</shortcode>
<para>The electronegativity difference between two atoms can be used to determine what type of bonding exists between the atoms. The table below lists the approximate values. Although we have given ranges here bonding is more like a spectrum than a set of boxes.</para>
