           <section type="section">
    <title>Energy and bonding</title>
    <shortcode>ESBMJ</shortcode>
<para>As we saw earlier in the chapter we can show the energy changes that occur as atoms come together (Figure <link target-id="fig:bonding:energy1"/>). Shown below is the same image but this time with two extra pieces of information: the bond energy and the bond length.</para>
